ipli by apprais percentag of recoveri actual percentag of recoveri apprais percentag of recoveri is base on the blueprint of the mine approv in accord with relev state regul where a mine enterpris is requir to prepar onli a mine plan instead of a blueprint the percentag of recoveri shall be determin by the depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc manag under the local peopl s govern at and abov the counti level togeth with other relev depart where miner right fee for certain miner cannot be calcul in accord with the provis of the first and second paragraph of thi articl the depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc under the state council shall develop separ formula togeth with the state council s financ depart articl 6 miner right fee shall be collect in accord with the rate provid for in the appendix of these regul adjust of miner right fee shall be made jointli by the state council financ depart and the state council depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc and shall be implement after it is submit to and approv by the state council articl 7 miner right fee shall be collect jointli by the depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc and the financ depart where a mine is locat in an administr district at the counti level miner right fee shall be collect by the depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc under the peopl s govern of the counti where the mine ar locat where the area of a mine extend beyond an administr district abov the counti level miner right fee shall be collect by the depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc of the peopl s govern at the next higher level where the area of a mine extend beyond an administr district at the provinci level or is in the territori water of the peopl s republ of china or water under it jurisdict miner right fee shall be collect by the depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc of the provinci peopl s govern author by the state council depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc articl 8 peopl with min