FBIS4-50570: bfn rule for implement of the miner resourc law of the peopl s republ of china rule text beij 30 mar xinhua chapter i gener principl articl 1 these rule have been formul in accord with relev provis of the miner resourc law of the peopl s republ of china articl 2 miner resourc form by geolog reaction ar natur solid liquefi or ga resourc with util valu variou or and categori of miner resourc have been list under the rule detail catalogu on variou miner resourc befor announc newli discov miner relev depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc under the state council shall obtain the state council s approv articl 3 miner resourc belong to the state the state s ownership over miner resourc deposit underground or on land remain unchang no matter who ha the ownership or land us right of the land where the miner resourc ar deposit the state council shall execut ownership of miner resourc on the state s behalf the state council shall entrust relev depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc under the state council to administ unifi manag in alloc miner resourc across china articl 4 peopl who prospect or extract miner resourc within prc territori and other water under it jurisdict must abid by the miner resourc law of the peopl s republ of china hereaft refer to as the miner resourc law and these rule articl 5 the state shall implement a system wherebi permit ar requir to prospect or extract miner resourc to prospect miner resourc in accord with the relev provis peopl must appli for regist and obtain a permit and the right to do so to extract miner resourc in accord with the relev provis peopl must appli for regist and obtain a permit and the right to do so zone or plot demarc along latitudin and longitudin line shall be the basic unit for prospect or extract miner resourc relev depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc under the state council shall formul the specif provis articl 6 mean of the follow term list in the miner resourc law and these rule the right to prospect miner resourc mean a permit and the right to prospect miner resourc ha been obtain in accord with the relev provis unit or individu acquir a permit to prospect miner resourc ar term as peopl with prospect right the right to extract miner resourc mean a permit and the right to extract miner resourc and miner product ha been obtain in accord with the relev provis unit or individu acquir a permit to extract them ar term peopl with mine right specif miner that ar extract under protect state regul ar miner that ar specifi by the state council base on the requir of facilit nation econom construct and develop high technolog and on their scarciti and valu and that ar extract with the approv of relev state council depart in accord with state plan state design mine zone ar miner resourc distribut zone demarc by the state base on given construct plan and miner resourc program in an effort to develop larg and medium mine mine zone that ar of kei import to the nation economi ar miner resourc preserv zone that ar specifi by the state in an effort to develop the nation economi that ar not yet incorpor into nation construct program and that have abund and qualiti deposit and good prospect for develop articl 7 the state allow foreign compani enterpris and other econom organ and individu to prospect or extract miner resourc within prc territori and other water under it jurisdict in accord with relev prc law and administr regul articl 8 the author in charg of geologi and miner resourc under the state council shall be respons for overse and manag the explor and extract of miner resourc throughout the countri relev compet depart under the state council shall share the work accord to their function delin by the state council and assist the author in charg of geologi and miner resourc under the state council in overse and manag the explor and extract of miner resourc depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc under provinci autonom region and municip peopl s govern shall be respons for overse and manag the explor and extract of miner resourc in their administr divis relev depart under provinci autonom region and municip peopl s govern shall assist the depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc at correspond level in overse and manag the explor and extract of miner resourc the peopl s govern of citi which have been divid into district autonom prefectur peopl s govern and counti level peopl s govern as well as their depart in charg of miner resourc shall overse and manag in accord with the law state own mine enterpris set up with the approv of peopl s govern at correspond level as well as collect own mine enterpris privat run mine enterpris individu miner and unit and individu carri out prospect work in their administr divis thei shall protect the legitim right and interest of holder of prospect and mine right depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc at higher level have the right to modifi or nullifi the illeg or inappropri action of their counterpart at lower level in manag and administ the explor and extract of miner resourc chapter ii registr for the explor of miner resourc and examin and approv of mine applic articl 9 in prospect for miner resourc matter relat to applic examin and approv and the registr of prospect activ shall be handl in accord with relev state council provis on the registr and manag of activ in prospect for miner resourc in prospect for specif type of miner matter relat to applic examin and approv and the registr of prospect activ shall be handl in accord with relev state council provis articl 10 in extract miner resourc state own mine enterpris shall attend to matter pertain to applic examin and approv and mine registr in accord with state council provis on mine registr and manag in attend to these same matter with regard to the extract of miner in state plan mine area and in mine area of great valu to the nation economi as well as the extract of specif type of miner prescrib by the state for protect min