 built 3 miner prospect data and approv oper plan and 4 necessari condit for safe product and environment protect measur chapter iii prospect of miner resourc articl 15 the state shall work out unifi plan for prospect of miner resourc medium and long rang plan for prospect miner resourc nationwid shall be map out under the guidanc of the state council depart in charg of plan and by the depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc in accord with the medium and long rang plan for nation econom and social develop nation and provinci autonom region and municip annual plan for prospect miner resourc shall be map out respect by the state council s depart and the provinci autonom region and municip peopl s govern depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc in coordin with the relev depart and in accord with nation medium and long rang miner resourc prospect plan and shall be implement after approv by the plan depart of the peopl s govern at the correspond level where law provid separ stipul for the author to review and approv prospect plan thei shall be formul accord to the relev law articl 16 holder of prospect right shall be entitl to the follow right 1 carri out prospect work within the area time frame and target prescrib by prospect licens 2 erect power and water suppli and commun line within prospect area and their peripher area which howev shall not interfer with or crippl the exist power and water suppli facil and commun line 3 free passag of prospect area and their peripher area 4 temporari us of land to meet oper need 5 prioriti of prospect right to newli discov miner or in prospect area 6 prioriti in mine right to miner resourc in prospect area and 7 self market of miner product recycl from approv prospect design except for those to be purchas uniformli by unit design by the state council when holder of prospect right exercis the right list in the preced paragraph thei should observ stipul of relev law and regul requir approv or complet of other formal to do so 