ountri and a ration delimit of the jurisdict with which the central author and the provinci autonom region and municip peopl s govern can examin and approv or carri out the exploit of miner resourc articl 26 the miner resourc exploit program mean a program that provid unifi plan for the layout of exploit and develop of mine area the miner resourc exploit program shall be divid into the sector exploit program and the region exploit program the sector miner resourc exploit program shall be drawn up and implement by relev compet depart of the state council base on the miner resourc assign to the respect depart under the nation miner resourc program the region miner resourc exploit program shall be drawn up and implement by the provinci autonom region and municip peopl s govern base on the miner resourc assign to the respect provinc autonom region or municip under the nation miner resourc program these govern shall also make unifi plan to ration delimit the jurisdict with which the peopl s govern at the provinci citi and counti level can examin and approv or carri out the exploit of miner resourc the sector and region miner resourc exploit program shall be report and submit to the state council depart in charg of plan and administr and of geologi and miner resourc for the record the state council depart in charg of plan and administr and of geologi and miner resourc shall correct ani sector exploit program or region exploit program that ar inconsist with the nation miner resourc program articl 27 to establish chang or revok the statu of a state design mine zone or a mine zone of kei import to the nation economi relev state council depart shall make a propos with detail report on it miner resourc and verifi data and inform after examin and approv the propos depart in charg of plan administr and miner resourc under the state council shall jointli inform in write the relev counti level peopl s govern within 30 dai of receipt of the notic the counti level peopl s govern sha