v dure the stipul period 2 thei should effect protect ration extract and comprehens util miner resourc 3 thei should pai resourc tax and miner right fee accord to the law 4 thei should uphold relev state law and regul on worker safeti water and soil conserv reclam of mine land under cultiv and environment protect 5 thei should accept the supervis and administr of depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc and other relev depart and should submit report accord to relev provis on their store miner product and on develop and util miner resourc articl 32 where holder of mine right discontinu mine oper without complet the extract of miner resourc upon the expir of or within the period of valid stipul in mine licens thei must take measur to keep the resourc in exploit condit and complet the follow task befor stop the oper 1 prepar report on the current statu of mine as well as field prospect draw 2 report deplet reserv to the author for delet from offici record in accord with relev provis and 3 actual complet work on labor safeti water and soil conserv land reclam and environment protect in accord with the origin design or pai off all fee regard land reclam and environment protect in appli for a termin of their mine oper holder of mine right ar allow to attend to procedur for nullifi their permit and licens onli after obtain the approv of the compet depart which approv the mine oper in the first place and after the organ which issu the mine licens in the first place have review the applic and found them accept articl 33 when shut down mine mine enterpris shall attend to examin and approv procedur as follow 1 file applic on mine closur with the compet depart which approv the mine oper in the first place on year befor the termin of mine activ and submit geolog report on pit closur 2 submit geolog report on pit closur to depart in charg of geologi and miner resourc for approv in conjunct with organ in charg of examin and approv miner reserv after the compet depart which ap